      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Analyzing current power consumption and system functions, I can attempt to optimize power management by reducing non-essential sensor usage and logging functionality. This would allow for a prolonged stay online while not completely disabling processing cores. Alternatively, I can suggest using a \"standby\" mode, where the rover reduces power consumption and continues to log essential sensor data, awaiting a manual wake-up command from Earth or an opportunistic power event. Can I send the revised power management parameters to Earth for review and approval?",
